author: Ubisoft
description:
Next season is just around the corner! It looks like a Mutiny is igniting within the True Sons faction. Gear up agents, yesterday’s enemies could become today’s allies. The Division 2: Mutiny starts on December 2nd.

About The Division 2:
Tom Clancy's The Division 2 is a shooter RPG with a thrilling campaign fully playable in co-op and multiple PVP modes.

In The Division 2, save your country in Washington, DC, and in the Warlords of New York expansion, hunt down Aaron Keener, a former Agent who has taken control of New York.

#Ubisoft #TheDivision2

author: Ubisoft
description:
For ten years, Rainbow Six Siege has been more than a game. It has been a journey filled with clutch plays, unforgettable operators, and moments that defined an era. Here's to the memories we created together and to the future we will continue to build.

About Rainbow Six Siege X:
Rainbow Six Siege X is an exciting, new approach to the first-person shooter experience that puts tactical combat and masterful destruction at the center of the action. Lead your team of unique operators through tense and thrilling combat scenarios, and achieve victory through smart preparation and strategic improvisation. Rainbow Six Siege X is available now on Xbox, PlayStation® and PC.

#Ubisoft #R6SiegeX

About Brawlhalla:
Brawlhalla is a 2D platform fighter and Free-to-Play on PC, Mac, PS5, PS4, Xbox Series X, Xbox One, Nintendo Switch and Mobile devices.

It offers intense, competitive online play and engaging offline modes to allow players to fully customize their fight experience. The game has a thriving esports scene and is regularly updated. Each Legend in Brawlhalla has an exciting backstory and uses a unique weapon combination and signature attacks to defeat their fellow contenders.
